INSERT INTO `aggregator_item` VALUES ('78','4','Two Minnesota HIEs Merge','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78077','','The Minnesota Health Information Exchange, LLC (MN HIE) has consolidated business operations with the Community Health Information Collaborative (CHIC)','1314889641','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78077'),('79','4','Article Explores Need for Interoperability between HIEs and Providers\' EHRs','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78078','','Last month in its August edition and on its website, Healthcare Informatics magazine published an article examining how HIE leaders are working to ensure interoperability between HIEs and providers\' EHRs.','1314889700','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78078'),('80','4','NJHCIC: From Concept to Reality','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78079','','This article is the first in a series documenting the development of the New Jersey Health Care Innovation Center (NJHCIC).','1314889761','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78079'),('81','4','BluePrint Innovation Summit Series—Call for Participant Applications for Mid-West Summit Now Open','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78080','','The BluePrint Health IT Innovation Exchange Summit Series features regional events where healthcare providers are matched up with innovative companies through \"speed dating\" sessions to establish pilot programs in alignment with the current innovation initiatives of HHS and ONC.','1314889821','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78080'),('82','4','Viewpoint: Engaging Physicians with HIE','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78081','','Last month\'s issue of HIELight