INSERT INTO `aggregator_item` VALUES ('83','4','HIE Formation Part VII: Defining Your Objectives; Measuring your Progress ','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78082','','In this series of monthly articles, based in part on their recently published book, the authors discuss current HIE related events and leading practices within the context of forming an HIE initiative in your state, region or community.','1314889965','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78082'),('84','4','Legal Corner: Accurate Patient Records Matching&mdash;Time for HIE Leadership','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78083','','The realization of broader scale electronic HIE has exacerbated the concern for establishing means to ensure accuracy of matching patients to their data that is accessed through an exchange.','1314890066','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78083'),('85','4','Public Health and HIE: The Gotcha of Data Submission','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78084','','Meaningful Use is a great opportunity for public health to leverage an activity with great momentum to further its own interoperability goals and needs.','1314890142','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78084'),('86','4','HIMSS Analytics EMR Adoption Model Now Part of US News Most Connected Hospitals','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78085','','Top hospitals ranked by US News and World Report received Stage 6 and 7 recognition per the HIMSS Analytics EMRAM scale.','1314895041','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78085'),('87','4','It’s Not Too Late to Register for the Policy Summit!','http://www.himss.org/ASP/ContentRedirector.asp?type=HIMSSNewsItem&ContentId=78086','','Thinking about joining us 