162','0','Viewpoint: Engaging Physicians with HIE','Last month\'s issue of HIELights highlighted a new HIMSS HIE Toolkit white paper (members only) titled Engaging Physicians with HIE. The white paper offers a brief overview of the value of HIE, followed by a discussion of strategies for using a community HIE and participating in directed exchange even without an EHR in the practice.','Last month\'s issue of HIELights highlighted a new HIMSS HIE Toolkit white paper (members only) titled Engaging Physicians with HIE. The white paper offers a brief overview of the value of HIE, followed by a discussion of strategies for using a community HIE and participating in directed exchange even without an EHR in the practice.','','1315927988','2');
