ing about joining us in Washington D.C. on September 14-15 for HIMSS 10th Annual Policy Summit? Registration is just $95, and includes breakfast, lunch, a reception, terrific educational resources, networking opportunities, and Congressional appointments pre-arranged by HIMSS staff. In addition to an exciting agenda on Thursday, featuring a keynote speech from Representative Michael Burgess, MD (R-TX) and a discussion of HIMSS’ 2011 requests to Congress, Summit attendees are invited to the National Health IT Week Networking and Awards Reception on September 14th. Awards to be presented include the Modern Healthcare/HIMSS CEO IT Achievement Awards, the CHIME State Advocacy Award for CIO Leadership, the HIMSS Federal Leadership Award, and the HIMSS State Leadership Award.','Thinking about joining us in Washington D.C. on September 14-15 for HIMSS 10th Annual Policy Summit? Registration is just $95, and includes breakfast, lunch, a reception, terrific educational resources, networking opportunities, and Congressional appointments pre-arranged by HIMSS staff. In addition to an exciting agenda on Thursday, featuring a keynote speech from Representative Michael Burgess, MD (R-TX) and a discussion of HIMSS’ 2011 requests to Congress, Summit attendees are invited to the National Health IT Week Networking and Awards Reception on September 14th.','','1315927988','2');
INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES ('38168','38168','0','National Indian Regional Extension Center Efforts Go Live in California','Last week the National Indian Health Board Regional Extension Center and the Office of the National Coordinator for Health IT approved the California Rural Indian Health Board to serve as a subrecipient for the American Indian/Alaska Native National Regional Extension Center (National Indian REC).','Last week the National Indian Health Board Regional Extension Center and the Office of the National Coordinator for Health IT approved the California Rural Indian Health Board to serve as a subrecipient for the American Indian/Alaska Native National Regional Extension Center (National Indian REC).','','1315927988','2'),('38169','38169','0','HIMSS Publishes Fact Sheet on Congressional ‘Super Committee’','HIMSS has prepared a fact sheet on the new congressional ‘super committee,’ including potential implications of committee deliberations for health IT.','HIMSS has prepared a fact sheet on the new congressional ‘super committee,’ including potential implications of committee deliberations for health IT.','','1315927988','2'),('38170','38170','0','Meet Our Members: Martha Dameron, RN, MSN, FHIMSS','Martha Dameron, RN, MSN, FHMSS, is the chair of the HIMSS Chapter Advocacy Roundtable (CAR). She also serves as a career consultant in the field of health IT , working with healthcare facilities, hospitals and IPAs to assist in vendor evaluation and selection for healthcare information systems (HIS), and electronic healthcare record (EHR) and electronic medical record (EMR) systems. Dameron’s role also includes consulting for change management, strategic planning and implementation processes with the end user.','Martha Dameron, RN, MSN, FHMSS, is the chair of the HIMSS Chapter Advocacy Roundtable (CAR). She also serves as a career consultant in the field of health IT , working with healthcare facilities, hospitals and IPAs to assist in vendor evaluation and selection for healthcare information systems (HIS), and electronic healthcare record (EHR) and electronic medical record (EMR) systems. Dameron’s role also includes consulting for change management, strategic planning and implementation processes with the end user.','','1315927988','2');
INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES ('38171','38171','0','HIMSS Davies Award Honors Two Public Health System Winners for Health IT Excellence','Whether it’s a tracking report on the spread of a flu virus or information on a food-borne illness related to a specific food product served in a restaurant or stocked on grocery store shelves, electronic public health systems track disease trends and frequency to ensure good health for populations of citizens of a particular state or region.','Whether it’s a tracking report on the spread of a flu virus or information on a food-borne illness related to a specific food product served in a restaurant or stocked on grocery store shelves, electronic public health systems track disease trends and frequency to ensure good health for populations of citizens of a particular state or region.','','1315927988','2'),('38172','38172','0','HIMSS Latino Community Launches Web Site','HIMSS is excited to launch the new landing page for our HIMSS Latino Community.','HIMSS is excited to launch the new landing page for our HIMSS Latino Community.','','1315927988','2'),('38173','38173','0','Have You Registered for the Policy Summit Yet?','If you plan to join us in Washington D.C. on September 14-15 for HIMSS 10th Annual Policy Summit, please note that the HIMSS hotel block closes TODAY! In addition to an exciting agenda on Thursday, featuring a keynote speech from Representative Michael Burgess, MD (R-TX), Summit attendees are invited to the National Health IT Week Networking and Awards Reception on September 14th. Awards to be presented include the Modern Healthcare CEO IT Achievement Awards, the CHIME State Advocacy Award for CIO Leadership, the HIMSS Federal Leadership Award, and the HIMSS State Leadership Award. RSVPs are requested.','If you plan to join us in Washington D.C. on September 14-15 for HIMSS 10th Annual Policy Summit, please note that the HIMSS hotel block closes TODAY! In addition to an exciting agenda on Thursday, featuring a 